    <!--default color-->

    <!--A touch feedback drawable may contain multiple child layers,
    including a special mask layer that is not drawn to the screen.
    A single layer may be set as the mask from XML by specifying its android:id value as mask-->


    <!--android:id="@android:id/mask"表示去除其他层的layer效果,比如去掉按钮按下Z方向动画，
